CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 22, 1955, pg. 12, reads: "New Diamond Market - ...Exterior view...The management of the New Diamond Market welcomes you to share in their giant twenty-fifth anniversary celebration beginning Friday, Oct. 21, through Dec. 6 - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Shoppers walking in front of Original New Diamond Market, with neon sign and advertisements for "Irish Hams and Bacon" Forbes Avenue, Downtown
